\c 139
\s Jehovha Muzivi noMuoni wezvese
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha, imwi makandinzvera, nokundiziva.
\v 2 Munoziva kugara kwangu pasi nokusimuka kwangu, Munonzwisisa kufunga kwangu muri kure.
\v 3 Munopepeta kufamba kwangu nokurara kwangu pasi, Munoziva nzira dzangu dzese.
\v 4 Nokuti shoko risati ravapo parurimi rwangu: Tarirai, imwi Jehovha, matoriziva rese.
\v 5 Makandikomberedza shure kwangu nemberi, Nokuisa ruoko rwenyu pamusoro pangu.
\v 6 Kuziva \add kwakadai\add* kunondishamisa kwazvo; Zviri kumusoro, handigoni kusvikira kwazviri.
\v 7 Ndingaendepiko ndibve pamweya wenyu? Kana ndingatizirepiko ndibve pamberi penyu?
\v 8 Kana ndikakwira kudenga muripo; Kana ndikazviwarira nhovo paSheori, tarirai muripowo.
\v 9 Kana ndikabhururuka namapapiro amangwanani, Ndikanogara pamigumo yegungwa;
\v 10 Naipapowo ruoko rwenyu ruchandifambisa, Ruoko rwenyu rworudyi ruchandifambisa,
\v 11 Kana ndikati: Zvirokwazvo, rima richandifukidza, Chiedza chinondikomberedza chichava sousiku;
\v 12 Kunyange rima haringandivanzi kwamuri, Asi usiku hunopenya samasikati; Rima nechiedza zvakafanana.
\v 13 Nokuti imwi makaumba itsvo dzangu; Makandiruka mudumbu ramai vangu.
\v 14 Ndichakuvongai; nokuti ndakaitwa nomutowo unotyisa unoshamisa; Mabasa enyu anoshamisa; Mweya wangu unozviziva kwazvo.
\v 15 mafupa angu akange asina kuvanzwa kwamuri, Panguva yandakaitwa pakavanda, Pakuumbwa kwangu nenjere panzvimbo dzezasi dzapasi.
\v 16 Meso enyu akaona muviri wangu uchigere kukwaniswa, Zvese zvakange zvakanyorwa murugwaro rwenyu, zuva rimwe nerimwe rokuumbwa kwazvo, Kusati kwava nechimwe chazvo.
\v 17 Yakakosha sei kwandiri mirangariro yenyu, Mwari! Yakakura sei pakuverengwa kwayo!
\v 18 Kana ndikaiverenga, ingapfuura jecha pakuwanda; Kana ndichipepuka, ndichinemi.
\v 19 Dai muchiuraya henyu vakaipa, Mwari; Naizvozvo ibvai kwandiri, imwi vanhu veropa.
\v 20 Nokuti vanokutaurirai zvakaipa, Vavengi venyu vanoreva zita renyu pasina.
\v 21 Ko ini handivengi avo vanokuvengai here, Jehovha? Handine shungu here navanokumukirai?
\v 22 Ndinovavenga nembengo huru; Vava vavengi vangu.
\v 23 Ndinzverei, Mwari, muzive moyo wangu; Ndiidzei, muzive ndangariro dzangu;
\v 24 Mutarire kana panenzira yakaipa mandiri, Mundifambise munzira isingaperi.
